name: Lancephorhynchus
desc:
[ Pendulum Effect ] 
If a Normal Monster you control attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent.
[ Monster Effect ] 
''This primordial species survived extinction by evolving an offensive lance that can pierce anything, although its diet still consists mainly of fish.''
